    dc:description "Fig. 18. Parabopyrella symmetros n. sp., holotype female (CIEAL800505) (A–G): A. Dorsal view. B. Ventral view. C. Right maxilliped, external view. D. Right side of barbula. E. Right oostegite 1, external view. F. Right oostegite 1, internal view. G. Right pereopod 7. Allotype male (CIEAL800506) (H, I): H. Dorsal view. I. Ventral view. Scale: 2 mm (A, B); 1 mm (C, D); 1.5 mm (E, F); 0.55 mm (G); 0.5 mm (H, I)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4612566/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

